data.description: Spacious Pueblo West tri-level home with mountain views and plenty of room for all your furry friends and recreational vehicles! If you love everything outdoors and want plenty of elbow room from your neighbors, this is the home for you. Walk in to the open-concept main floor with vaulted ceilings and all new wood grain design tile floors that tie the entire space together. The kitchen is roomy and functional, with newer range oven and great views of the common areas. Convenient breakfast bar as well as ample dining space. Upstairs you will find the primary suite with a walk-in closet, private attached full bathroom and breathtaking views. Two more bedrooms and a full bath complete the upstairs. The garden level family room has a built-in TV stand and cozy gas fireplace. Also on the lower level is a fourth bedroom with built-in desks and shelving, another full bath and large laundry room. The fully fenced and cross fenced over acre property features a large deck/patio, kids playground, and two storage sheds. Another cover/loafing shed structure is also out back. The patio has plenty of room for seating and grilling and is durable composite material. There is so much potential to add garages, barns, any type of outbuilding that you'd like in the back yard or on the ample additional parking areas to the right side of the home. Features of this home include: Central A/C, 2017 septic system, newer water heater, sump pump & vapor barrier in crawl space. 5 mins from the reservoir.
